{"ts":"2026-07-06T21:09:28.492Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/474\n\nHonor `--limit` in hybrid search mode (parity with keyword mode), applied after hybrid rank fusion so the top-N fused results are returned. Preserve the deterministic limit=0 empty-result semantics established in pm-6mn1."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-alnj"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-474: pm search --limit support in hybrid mode"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Dogfood GH-474: hybrid search can return many results and --limit (available in keyword mode) is not honored/available in hybrid mode, breaking agent token budgets. Duplicate check: searched hybrid search limit — pm-6mn1 (closed, M4) covered limit=0 determinism only; this is general --limit support in hybrid mode."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Feature"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-experience","area:search","gh-issue","token-efficiency"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-06T21:09:28.492Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-06T21:09:28.492Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":90},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"pm search --mode hybrid honors --limit identically to keyword mode (applied after fusion ranking); documented in help/contracts; spec covers limit interaction with hybrid result fusion including limit=0 determinism from pm-6mn1"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-ydp6"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"low"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b